data.name: Pumpkin Seed Salad Topping
data.quickTastyDescription: A crunchy and nutritious topping that adds flavor and texture to any salad!
detailedCookingInstructions: In a skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat.
Add the pumpkin seeds and stir to coat them in the oil.
Sprinkle in the salt, paprika, and garlic powder.
Toast the seeds for about 5 minutes, stirring frequently, until they are golden brown and fragrant.
Remove from heat and let cool before using as a salad topping.
